    _descFinnish: "Kun jokin minulle t\xE4rke\xE4 on uhattuna, puolustan sit\xE4
      hinnalla mill\xE4 hyv\xE4ns\xE4."
    _descEnglish: 'When something important to me is threatened, I defend it at any
      cost. '
