    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 590ee8632f341a34bb09d4e293205e56, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "Edustan kaipausta ja tarvetta tulla hyv\xE4ksytyksi. Kurotan kohti
      toisia ja etsin samalla itse\xE4ni."
    _descEnglish: I embody longing and the need to be accepted. I reach toward others
      while searching for myself.
