    _cornerIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4465914b30e24cd4d8b1c38034b54eaf, type: 3}
    _character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d90e49211f9bcf940862f95c96d7df61, type: 3}
    _descFinnish: "Vaatimukset ovat kahleita vapauteni ymp\xE4rill\xE4. Voimani on
      p\xE4\xE4t\xF6ksess\xE4 olla tekem\xE4tt\xE4 mit\xE4\xE4n."
    _descEnglish: Demands are chains wrapped around my freedom. My power lies in
      the decision to do nothing.
